content: And that makes some sense, you had variance in a certain things occurring during the first quarter that made it sometimes a little more difficult as things we're opening, closing, but clearly in April, the world changed a bit and I think our agents clearly combined what they learned during the pandemic and want to keep that going from an ease of dealing with customers in a more virtual way, but also had the added benefit of being a little more connected live and in-person with those educators.
